evi strauss  co filed a lawsuit against abercrombie  fitch and the rl corporation in july  for trademark infringement it alleged that the separate retailers used levis trademarked pocket design of connected arches in the design of some of their respective products south african polo trademark issues the polo brand sold in south africa is not affiliated with the ralph lauren brand an independent south african company trademarked the polo name and logo in south africa filippa hamilton photo controversy in  ralph lauren apologized for digitally retouching a photograph of model filippa hamilton to make her look thinner hamilton also claims that she was fired by ralph lauren a few days later another models photo was also digitally retouched adding to the row of models referencesedit  ralph lauren stores ralph lauren media retrieved june     a b c d e ralph lauren reports fourth quarter and full year fiscal  results united states securities and exchange commission april     number of employees of polo ralph lauren worldwide from  to  statista retrieved june     ralph lauren the patriarch of fashions rise from ragtrader to american royalty the independent  retrieved    ralph lauren through the years the new york times retrieved    exploring the world of fashion in film the independent  retrieved    ralph lauren the emperor has clothes fortune  retrieved    ralph lauren corp rl ipo nasdaq retrieved    ralph lauren creates his clubhouse new york times  retrieved    tabuchi hiroko friedman vanessa  september  ralph lauren creator of fashion empire is stepping down as ceo ny times retrieved  september    end of an era ralph lauren is stepping down as ceo of his company esquire  retrieved    gensler lauren ralph lauren ceo to depart over different views with founder shares tumble forbes retrieved    badkar mamta may   ralph lauren adjusted earnings top estimates as it bridles discounts financial times united kingdom retrieved may     reuters  bloomberg  fortune  the wall street